cyUyMFNpbmdhcG9yZXxlbnwxfDB8fHwxNzgzNTg3MzMyfDA&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fit=max&fm=jpg&q=80&w=1080","credit":"Hu Chen"},"description":"Singapore's iconic waterfront district featuring the world-famous Marina Bay Sands hotel, ArtScience Museum, and stunning skyline views. This is the heart of modern Singapore and essential for experiencing the city's contemporary culture, dining, and entertainment scene."},{"rank":2,"name":"Sentosa Island","placeId":"sentosa_island","regionId":"west","regionName":"West Region","image":{"index":0,"assetPath":"","isLocal":false,"url":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1662385834577-0c6628d57eab?ixid=M3w5NTU4NjF8MHwxfHNlYXJjaHwxfHxTZW50b3NhJTIwSXNsYW5kJTIwYmVhY2glMjByZXNvcnR8ZW58MXwwfHx8MTc4MzYwMDM4NHww&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fit=max&fm=jpg&q=80&w=1080","credit":"Aparna Johri"},"description":"Singapore's premier island resort destination featuring world-class attractions including Universal Studios, S.E.A. Aquarium, and pristine beaches. It offers diverse entertainment, water sports, and leisure activities making it essential for any visitor to the west region."},{"rank":3,"name":"Orchard Road","placeId":"orchard_road","regionId":"central","regionName":"Central Region","image":{"index":0,"assetPath":"","isLocal":false,"url":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559329187-324b79e997b0?ixid=M3w5NTU4NjF8MHwxfHNlYXJjaHwxfHxPcmNoYXJkJTIwUm9hZCUyMFNpbmdhcG9yZXxlbnwxfDB8fHwxNzgzNTg3MzUyfDA&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fit=max&fm=jpg&q=80&w=1080","credit":"K8"},"description":"Singapore's premier shopping district stretching over two kilometers with world-class malls, designer boutiques, restaurants, and entertainment venues. It's the ultimate destination for shopping, dining, and experiencing modern Singapore's urban lifestyle."},{"rank":4,"name":"Gardens by the Bay","placeId":"gardens_by_the_bay","regionId":"central","regionName":"Central Region","image":{"index":0,"assetPath":"","isLocal":false,"url":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1663411409190-4ea7f1ea76f5?ixid=M3w5NTU4NjF8MHwxfHNlYXJjaHwxfHxHYXJkZW5zJTIwYnklMjB0aGUlMjBCYXklMjBTdXBlcnRyZWVzfGVufDF8MHx8fDE3ODM1ODczMzV8MA&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fit=max&fm=jpg&q=80&w=1080","credit":"Joshua Kettle"},"description":"A stunning 101-hectare garden featuring iconic Supertrees, themed gardens, and conservatories showcasing plants from around the world. It's a masterpiece of modern landscape design and one of Asia's most visited attractions."},{"rank":5,"name":"Chinatown","placeId":"chinatown","regionId":"central","regionName":"Central Region","image":{"index":0,"assetPath":"","isLocal":false,"url":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1536163713675-42cf53cbd4f5?ixid=M3w5NTU4NjF8MHwxfHNlYXJjaHwxfHxDaGluYXRvd24lMjBTaW5nYXBvcmV8ZW58MXwwfHx8MTc4MzU4NzM0MHww&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fit=max&fm=jpg&q=80&w=1080","credit":"Adrian Jakob"},"description":"A historic district filled with traditional shophouses, temples, bustling markets, and authentic Chinese restaurants and hawker stalls. This vibrant cultural neighborhood offers visitors a glimpse into Singapore's Chinese heritage and traditional street life."},{"rank":6,"name":"Universal Studios Singapore","placeId":"universal_studios_singapore","regionId":"sentosa","regionName":"Sentosa Island","image":{"index":0,"assetPath":"","isLocal":false,"url":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1696851108364-5341c14c49cf?ixid=M3w5NTU4NjF8MHwxfHNlYXJjaHwxfHxVbml2ZXJzYWwlMjBTdHVkaW9zJTIwU2luZ2Fwb3JlJTIwZW50cmFuY2V8ZW58MXwwfHx8MTc4MzU5MjA3M3ww&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fit=max&fm=jpg&q=80&w=1080","credit":"Akshay Janjire"},"description":"Southeast Asia's first major Hollywood theme park featuring themed lands with thrilling rides, shows, and attractions based on blockbuster films and franchises. It's the centerpiece attraction of Sentosa Island and a must-visit for families and thrill-seekers alike."},{"rank":7,"name":"East Coast Park","placeId":"east_coast_park","regionId":"east_coast","regionName":"East Coast","image":{"index":0,"assetPath":"","isLocal":false,"url":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1604228439910-354b9b5ab324?ixid=M3w5NTU4NjF8MHwxfHNlYXJjaHwxfHxFYXN0JTIwQ29hc3QlMjBQYXJrJTIwU2luZ2Fwb3JlJTIwYmVhY2h8ZW58MXwwfHx8MTc4MzU5MjEwM3ww&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fit=max&fm=jpg&q=80&w=1080","credit":"Christoph Theisinger"},"description":"Singapore's largest coastal park stretching 15 kilometres with sandy beaches, cycling tracks, and recreational facilities along the East Coast. It's the perfect place for swimming, picnicking, water sports, and enjoying seaside activities with stunning views of the Straits of Singapore."},{"rank":8,"name":"Merlion Park","placeId":"merlion_park","regionId":"marina_bay","regionName":"Marina Bay","image":{"index":0,"assetPath":"","isLocal":false,"url":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1509325124054-c11dd7576cbd?ixid=M3w5NTU4NjF8MHwxfHNlYXJjaHwxfHxNZXJsaW9uJTIwc3RhdHVlJTIwZm91bnRhaW58ZW58MXwwfHx8MTc4MzU5MjA1MXww&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fit=max&fm=jpg&q=80&w=1080","credit":"Uriel Soberanes"},"description":"Home to Singapore's iconic Merlion statue, a mythical creature symbolizing the nation's origins as a fishing village and its growth as a lion city. It remains one of Singapore's most photographed landmarks and offers excellent views of Marina Bay."},{"rank":9,"name":"Sentosa Beaches","placeId":"sentosa_beaches","regionId":"sentosa","regionName":"Sentosa Island","image":{"index":0,"assetPath":"","isLocal":false,"url":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1662385825401-d529115306a4?ixid=M3w5NTU4NjF8MHwxfHNlYXJjaHwxfHxTZW50b3NhJTIwQmVhY2hlcyUyMFNpbmdhcG9yZXxlbnwxfDB8fHwxNzg0MDMxMTk5fDA&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fit=max&fm=jpg&q=80&w=1080","credit":"Aparna Johri"},"description":"Sentosa Island features three pristine beaches including Siloso, Palawan, and Tanjong beaches with clear waters, beach clubs, and water sports facilities. They serve as Singapore's primary beach destinations attracting sun-seekers and water sports enthusiasts throughout the year."},{"rank":10,"name":"Singapore Zoo","placeId":"singapore_zoo","regionId":"north","regionName":"North Region","image":{"index":0,"assetPath":"","isLocal":false,"url":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1619262336523-3e217d76ab47?ixid=M3w5NTU4NjF8MHwxfHNlYXJjaHwxfHxTaW5nYXBvcmUlMjBab28lMjBhbmltYWxzfGVufDF8MHx8fDE3ODM3NTM4NDh8MA&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fit=max&fm=jpg&q=80&w=1080","credit":"Kyan Ng"},"description":"One of Asia's most prestigious zoological parks featuring over 2,800 animals and world-class exhibits set amidst lush tropical landscaping. It's a must-visit attraction for families and wildlife enthusiasts, offering educational experiences and close encounters with diverse species."}]}